- README file for building smbus library                                  -
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage
-----
Makefile update :
  1. Update the Makefile with epdm path in the  EPDM_HOME variable
  2. Enable respective flag based on the chip
     #ADD_FLAGS += -DPLP_APERTA2_SUPPORT
     #ADD_FLAGS += -DPLP_AGERA2_SUPPORT

To build smbus library, use the following commands:
  # make clean
  # make

smbus library (libsmbus.a) will be available inside lib folder
